<Layout title="Privacy Policy | FitJourney" description="Privacy Policy for FitJourney">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 14, 2025</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Survey responses:</strong> Answers you provide in our online survey (anonymous by default).</li>
    <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, device identifiers, and page usage metrics collected via analytics tools.</li>
    <li><strong>Contact information:</strong> Email address or other details if you opt in to follow-up research.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Product improvement:</strong> Analyze survey and usage data to develop and enhance FitJourney.</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Track site performance and user engagement through analytics tools.</li>
    <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> Serve relevant ads and measure ad performance using collected data.</li>
    <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Send research invitations or updates if you opt in.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
  <p>We use cookies, pixel tags, and similar technologies to collect technical data:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics tools:</strong> Standard site usage metrics.</li>
    <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> You can disable cookies in your browser settings or use browser plugins to opt out of analytics tracking.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Data Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> sell or rent personal data to third parties.</li>
    <li>We may share aggregated, non-identifiable survey results and analytics reports with partners or investors.</li>
    <li>Third-party advertising partners receive only the data necessary for ad measurement and optimization.</li>
    <li>We may disclose data if required by law or to respond to legal requests.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Anonymous survey responses:</strong> Retained indefinitely in aggregated form.</li>
    <li><strong>Technical & tracking data:</strong> Retained for up to 24 months for analytics and ad performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Opt-in contact info:</strong> Stored securely and deleted upon request.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You may have rights to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access & correct your personal data.</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your personal data.</li>
    <li>Opt out of cookies, analytics, or ad tracking.</li>
    <li>Obtain a copy of your data in a machine-readable format, where applicable.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@fitjourneyapp.ai">hello@fitjourneyapp.ai</a>.</p>

  <h2>7. Security</h2>
  <p>We implement industry-standard measures (encryption, access controls) to protect your data but cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

  <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy periodically. Changes will be posted here with an updated "Last updated" date.</p>
</Layout>
